    "Therefore, our judgment in this case was that the SLMs were correct at moderating them, and perhaps these comments were missed by human moderators.",
    "For FNs, we found that there were many comments related to topics such as wars, political controversies, and gender fluidity which the LLMs always moderate correctly, whereas the SLMs do not.",
